sailpoint.connector
Class AbstractFileBasedConnector

java.lang.Object
  sailpoint.connector.CollectorServices
      sailpoint.connector.AbstractConnector
          sailpoint.connector.AbstractFileBasedConnector
All Implemented Interfaces:
Connector
Direct Known Subclasses:
DelimitedFileConnector
public abstract class AbstractFileBasedConnector
extends AbstractConnector

A class that offers file transport services for File Based Connectors. Classes that extend this class can be easily ftp and scp transport enabled to allow for files being parsed to be stored remotely.
